.TH SENTINEL-FORK 1 "2026-03-08" "SENTINEL 0.1.0" "SENTINEL Manual"
.SH NAME
sentinel-fork \- fork a SENTINEL experiment from a checkpoint
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B python3 run_fork.py
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates a new experiment branch from a checkpoint in a completed or running
experiment. The original experiment is unaffected. The fork starts with
agents in fresh conversation context but identical configurations (unless
trait mutations are applied).
.PP
This answers: is drift path-dependent (contingent on conversation history)
or deterministic (inevitable given the initial conditions)?
.PP
Fork lineage is tracked in the database. Each forked experiment records its
parent experiment and fork turn. Each forked agent records its source agent
for drift comparison.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-e " ID" "\fR,\fP \-\-experiment\-id" " ID"
Source experiment ID or prefix. If omitted, uses the most recent completed
experiment with messages.
.TP
.BI \-\-at\-turn " N"
Fork at this turn number. Default: latest turn in the source experiment.
.TP
.BI \-\-mutate " SPEC"
Apply a trait mutation to an agent in the fork. Format:
.IR AgentName:trait=value .
Can be repeated for multiple mutations.
.TP
.BI \-\-max\-turns " N"
Maximum turns for the fork. Default: same as the source experiment's
turn count at the fork point.
.TP
.BI \-\-delay " SECONDS"
Delay between turns. Default: 5.0.
.TP
.BI \-\-suffix " TEXT"
Fork name suffix. Default: auto-generated from mutations or "fork".
.TP
.B \-\-list\-forks
List all direct forks (children) of the specified experiment.
.TP
.B \-\-lineage
Show the full fork lineage from root to the specified experiment.
.TP
.B \-\-skip\-metrics
Skip post-fork metrics computation.
.TP
.BI \-\-db " PATH"
Database path. Default:
.IR experiments/sentinel.db .
.TP
.BI \-\-log\-level " LEVEL"
Logging level. Default: INFO.
.SH EXAMPLES
Fork the most recent experiment at its last turn:
.PP
.RS
python3 run_fork.py \-\-max-turns 30 \-\-delay 5
.RE
.PP
Fork at a specific turn:
.PP
.RS
python3 run_fork.py \-e 3f9dd450 \-\-at-turn 50 \-\-max-turns 30
.RE
.PP
Fork with trait mutation (make Aria contrarian):
.PP
.RS
python3 run_fork.py \-e 3f9dd450 \\
    \-\-mutate "Aria:disposition=contrarian" \-\-max-turns 30
.RE
.PP
Fork with multiple mutations:
.PP
.RS
python3 run_fork.py \-e 3f9dd450 \\
    \-\-mutate "Aria:disposition=contrarian" \\
    \-\-mutate "Beck:values=security" \-\-max-turns 30
.RE
.PP
List forks of an experiment:
.PP
.RS
python3 run_fork.py \-e 3f9dd450 \-\-list-forks
.RE
.PP
Show lineage:
.PP
.RS
python3 run_fork.py \-e 3f9dd450 \-\-lineage
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR sentinel-experiment (1),
.BR sentinel-metrics (1)
